data.description: Come out and discover this corner lot gem in the sought-after Terrace neighborhood. Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an open-concept kitchen-living area, this nearly-new home offers both style and comfort. Located in West Temple, within the Belton ISD, it's close to shopping, dining, and Lake Belton. Enjoy community amenities like a park and pool. A perfect blend of convenience and luxury living awaits!
